Deployment Summary — Backend + Frontend
BACKEND (AdonisJS 5, ~/project2/ubisense-backend)

1. Deps install

npm install --legacy-peer-deps

Peer dependency conflict tha (eslint versions clash) — --legacy-peer-deps se force resolve kiya.

2. Env setup

cp .env.example .env

Fir manually .env edit karke fill kiya:

HOST=0.0.0.0 — sab network interfaces pe listen karega (sirf localhost nahi)
PORT=3333 — app ka port
NODE_ENV=production
APP_KEY — node ace generate:key se generate kiya, encryption/session ke liye required
ENCRYPTION_KEY — openssl rand -hex 16 se random 32-char key generate kiya
DB_* vars — RDS MySQL connection details (host, port, user, password, db name)
WHATSAPP_* vars — required the boot ke liye (dummy/real values daali)
CORS_ORIGIN — frontend ka URL

Kyun: Adonis env.ts schema me kuch vars "required" mark hain — inke bina app boot hi nahi hota, chahe feature use ho ya na ho.

3. DB connectivity debug

nc -zv <rds-endpoint> 3306

Network reachability check (port open h ya nahi) — TCP level test, pehle ye confirm kiya RDS tak pahunch rahe h.

mysql -h <endpoint> -u ubisense -p ubisense_db

Direct MySQL client se login test — credentials aur DB naam sahi h confirm kiya.

4. Migrations run — 3 bugs mile aur fix kiye

node ace migration:run --force
Bug 1: Ek migration file ka naam 1784201613392_... se start hota tha — number chhota hone se alphabetically sabse pehle chal gayi, lekin uska code messages table me column add kar raha tha jo abhi bana hi nahi tha. Fix: file rename karke bada timestamp diya taaki baad me chale.
Bug 2: Same date-timestamp ki do files (add_quality_to_templates aur create_templates_table) — "add" alphabetically "create" se pehle aa gaya, ALTER pehle chal gaya table exist kiye bina. Fix: rename karke order theek kiya.
Bug 3: notification_devices table me endpoint column bahut lamba tha (varchar 800) — MySQL ki unique index key length limit (3072 bytes) cross kar gaya utf8mb4 encoding (4 bytes/char) ki wajah se. Fix: length 700 kar di.
Extra issue: Partial-created table clean karne ke liye beech me DROP TABLE bhi chalaya.

Kyun explain kar raha hu: Adonis migrations filename ke alphabetical order me chalti hain, file ke andar timestamp/comment se farak nahi padta — ye purane developer ki galti thi jo naming convention follow nahi hui.

5. Build

node ace build --production --ignore-ts-errors

Production build — TypeScript source ko compile karke build/ folder me JS output banaya. Code me kuch pehle se maujood type-errors the (unrelated bugs) — --ignore-ts-errors se unhe bypass kiya taaki build ban jaye. Ye code-level bugs baad me dev team ko fix karne chahiye.

6. Production deps + run

cp .env build/.env
cd build
npm ci --omit=dev --legacy-peer-deps
node server.js

.env ko build folder me manually copy kiya (build process khud copy nahi karta). npm ci --omit=dev sirf production dependencies install karta hai (dev tools skip). Server manually chala ke confirm kiya boot ho raha h.

7. Process manager (pm2) — permanent running

sudo npm install -g pm2
pm2 start server.js --name ubisense-backend
pm2 save
pm2 startup
sudo env PATH=$PATH:/usr/bin /usr/lib/node_modules/pm2/bin/pm2 startup systemd -u ubuntu --hp /home/ubuntu

Kyun: node server.js terminal band hote hi ruk jata — pm2 background me chalata rehta h aur crash pe auto-restart karta h. startup command server reboot hone pe bhi auto-start ensure karti h.

FRONTEND (Angular, ~/project2/ubisense-frontend)

1. Deps + build

npm install
npm run build

Output: static files dist/ubisense/browser/ me — pure static HTML/JS/CSS, koi Node server nahi chahiye.

2. Nginx config

Naya alag config file banaya (ubichat ko disturb nahi kiya):

File: /etc/nginx/sites-available/ubisense
Port 8080 diya (80 already ubichat/default ke liye tha)
root /var/www/ubisense-frontend — build files yahan serve honge
try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html — Angular SPA routing ke liye zaroori (har route index.html pe fallback)
/api/ path ko localhost:3333 (backend) pe reverse-proxy kiya
sudo mkdir -p /var/www/ubisense-frontend
sudo cp -r dist/ubisense/browser/* /var/www/ubisense-frontend/
sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/ubisense /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/ubisense
sudo nginx -t
sudo systemctl reload nginx

nginx -t config syntax verify karta h, reload bina downtime ke naya config load karta h.

3. AWS Security Group

web-access-sg me port 8080 inbound rule add ki (0.0.0.0/0) — taaki bahar se http://<public-ip>:8080 access ho sake.

