Backend changes (code ya .env)

Code change hua (.ts files):

cd ~/project2/ubisense-backend
node ace build --production --ignore-ts-errors
cp .env build/.env
cd build
npm ci --omit=dev --legacy-peer-deps
pm2 restart ubisense-backend

Sirf .env change hua (code same):

cp ~/project2/ubisense-backend/.env ~/project2/ubisense-backend/build/.env
pm2 restart ubisense-backend
Frontend changes (code ya env)

Kisi bhi change ke baad (code ya environment.ts) — hamesha full rebuild:

cd ~/project2/ubisense-frontend
npm run build
sudo cp -r dist/ubisense/browser/* /var/www/ubisense-frontend/

Nginx restart/reload ki zarurat nahi — static files bas replace ho jaati h.